ement<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> type:","source":"If the RFQ is of the **Purchase agreement** type:"},{"content":"The RFQ is used for an agreement to purchase a specific quantity or value of product over time.","pos":[9199,9294]},{"content":"You must select the date range that applies to the purchase agreement and the name of the person who manages the purchase agreement.","pos":[9295,9427]},{"content":"When you accept a bid, a purchase agreement is generated.","pos":[9432,9489]},{"content":"You can create an RFQ from a purchase requisition only if the status of the purchase requisition is <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>In review<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> and you are assigned to do the next workflow task.","pos":[9491,9655],"source":"You can create an RFQ from a purchase requisition only if the status of the purchase requisition is **In review** and you are assigned to do the next workflow task."},{"content":"The lines in the purchase requisition are updated automatically as you accept lines from RFQ replies (bids) that you received from vendors.","pos":[9656,9795]},{"content":"You can't complete, reject, approve, or perform any other actions on the purchase requisition while the RFQ is in progress.","pos":[9796,9919]},{"content":"When you create an RFQ, you can select a specific solicitation type.","pos":[9923,9991]},{"content":"The solicitation type determines the set of scoring criteria that is used to score replies to the RFQ.","pos":[9992,10094]},{"content":"You can add a questionnaire to an RFQ case.","pos":[10098,10141]},{"content":"This questionnaire then appears on all replies after you send the RFQ.","pos":[10142,10212]},{"content":"There are three ways to select the vendors to add to an RFQ case:","pos":[10216,10281]},{"content":"Add the vendors one by one.","pos":[10287,10314]},{"content":"Search for all vendors that meet specific criteria.","pos":[10319,10370]},{"content":"Automatically add all vendors that are approved for the procurement categories that are used on 